flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 56A: Realtime and Notifications Business-Friendly Journey

  Start[Customer activity happens]
  Live[Platform sends live updates for order status, chat, and live events]
  Notify[System chooses the best notification channel]
  Delivered{Primary message delivered?}

  Fallback[Automatically switch to a backup channel]
  Seen[User receives the update and can act quickly]
  Trust[Delivery and read status are tracked for reliability]

  Start --> Live --> Notify --> Delivered
  Delivered -- Yes --> Seen --> Trust
  Delivered -- No --> Fallback --> Seen
